<subSubSection id="C32E653DFFD8FF9E37F6F9815D21A10D" pageId="5" pageNumber="590" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="8B8B36B6FFD8FF9E37F6F9815D21A10D" blockId="5.[151,1436,1338,1653]" pageId="5" pageNumber="590">
<emphasis id="B940EAA4FFD8FF9E37F6F9815F2DA129" bold="true" box="[199,315,1591,1617]" pageId="5" pageNumber="590">Remarks.</emphasis>
This is the first record of phoretic association between the mite and ants of the genus 
<taxonomicName id="4C344D35FFD8FF9E323BF9815B45A128" authorityName="Fabricius" authorityYear="1804" box="[1290,1363,1591,1616]" class="Insecta" family="Formicidae" genus="Lasius" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="5" pageNumber="590" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="B940EAA4FFD8FF9E323BF9815B45A128" box="[1290,1363,1591,1616]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="590">Lasius</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
. Also, this species is recorded from northern 
